channel.title: Shenantics
channel.description: Skxnky (Nick) and mcul_ (Shawn) are two guys who met on the Internet and are building a friendship together. Every week they get together for a fun, light-hearted, discussion where they learn something new about each other, get into stupid debates, and spend a lot of time reading Wikipedia articles out loud.
